# Sales Performance Dashboard (Power BI)

## Overview
This project presents an end-to-end Sales Performance Dashboard built in Power BI to analyse revenue, profit, and sales trends, and to identify key performance drivers.

## Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- Power Query
- DAX (basic measures)
- Excel

## Dataset
Publicly generated sales dataset with customer, product, regional, and time-based information. No personal or confidential data was used.

## Key Features
- KPI reporting (Sales, Profit, Quantity, Average Order Value)
- Sales and profit trends over time
- Category and product performance analysis
- Interactive slicers for region, segment, and year

## Key Insights
- Technology is the highest-performing category by sales
- Sales fluctuate over time with stronger performance in later periods
- A small number of products contribute a large share of total revenue

